{
  "id": "69a848d80e492e6a2f9ac589",
  "title": "Copilot CLIをインストールする",
  "created": 1772636377,
  "updated": 1772639159,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69a848d80e492e6a2f9ac589",
      "text": "Copilot CLIをインストールする",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772636377,
      "updated": 1772636377
    },
    {
      "id": "69a848d80000000000f05e57",
      "text": "インストール方法自体はここに載ってる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772636377,
      "updated": 1772636425
    },
    {
      "id": "69a849030000000000f05e59",
      "text": "\thttps://github.com/features/copilot/cli?locale=ja",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772636419,
      "updated": 1772636420
    },
    {
      "id": "69a848e30000000000f05e58",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772636387,
      "updated": 1772636387
    },
    {
      "id": "69a849090000000000f05e5a",
      "text": "[[インストールした後]]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772636426,
      "updated": 1772636450
    },
    {
      "id": "69a8490d0000000000f05e5b",
      "text": "[Copilot CLI]上で初回はログインする必要がある",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772636429,
      "updated": 1772636499
    },
    {
      "id": "69a8493a0000000000f05e5d",
      "text": "ログインの際セッション情報を平文保存するのはしんどいので、鍵管理ツールを入れるのが良い",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772636474,
      "updated": 1772636521
    },
    {
      "id": "69a849690000000000f05e5e",
      "text": "\t[WSL2 Ubuntuにkeyringを入れる]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772636522,
      "updated": 1772636565
    },
    {
      "id": "69a850f80000000000f05e7b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638457,
      "updated": 1772638457
    },
    {
      "id": "69a850fb0000000000f05e7d",
      "text": "[keyring]入れたら以下のコマンドでログインする",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638460,
      "updated": 1772639159
    },
    {
      "id": "69a851050000000000f05e7e",
      "text": "\t$ copilot login",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638470,
      "updated": 1772638474
    },
    {
      "id": "69a850f80000000000f05e7c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638457,
      "updated": 1772638457
    },
    {
      "id": "69a8491a0000000000f05e5c",
      "text": "色々やったら起動する",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772636443,
      "updated": 1772638439
    },
    {
      "id": "69a850e70000000000f05e7a",
      "text": "\t$ copilot --banner",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638439,
      "updated": 1772638478
    },
    {
      "id": "69a851100000000000f05e7f",
      "text": "\t\tbannerオプションは気分で外しても良い",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638481,
      "updated": 1772638494
    },
    {
      "id": "69a851240000000000f05e81",
      "text": "\t\t外しても起動アニメーションがなくなるだけ",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638501,
      "updated": 1772638510
    },
    {
      "id": "69a8511e0000000000f05e80",
      "text": "\t適当なプロンプトを入力すれば回答が返ってくる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638494,
      "updated": 1772638552
    },
    {
      "id": "69a851630000000000f05e84",
      "text": "\t`/quit`か`/exit`で終了",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638564,
      "updated": 1772638575
    },
    {
      "id": "69a851590000000000f05e82",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638554,
      "updated": 1772638554
    },
    {
      "id": "69a851590000000000f05e83",
      "text": "既定のモデルが[Claude]になっているので[Premium Request]をどんどん消化してしまう",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638554,
      "updated": 1772638707
    },
    {
      "id": "69a851f20000000000f05e86",
      "text": "\t毎回変えるのが鬱陶しければ環境変数を設定することで変更可能",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638707,
      "updated": 1772638730
    },
    {
      "id": "69a8520a0000000000f05e87",
      "text": "\t[fish shell]なら[config.fish]に以下のコードを入れておこう",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638730,
      "updated": 1772638749
    },
    {
      "id": "69a8521c0000000000f05e88",
      "text": "\t\tcode:config.fish",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638749,
      "updated": 1772638754
    },
    {
      "id": "69a852210000000000f05e89",
      "text": "\t\t set -Ux COPILOT_MODEL \"gpt-5-mini\"",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638754,
      "updated": 1772638754
    },
    {
      "id": "69a850540000000000f05e76",
      "text": "\t\t後ろのモデルは任意",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638293,
      "updated": 1772638775
    },
    {
      "id": "69a852370000000000f05e8b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638775,
      "updated": 1772638776
    },
    {
      "id": "69a852370000000000f05e8c",
      "text": "既定の状態だと何か質問しても英語で返答が返ってくる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638776,
      "updated": 1772638877
    },
    {
      "id": "69a8529d0000000000f05e8d",
      "text": "\t[カスタム命令]を入れて日本語で返すようにしておこう",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638878,
      "updated": 1772638892
    },
    {
      "id": "69a852b20000000000f05e8e",
      "text": "\t適当なエディターで以下のファイルを開く（なければ作る）",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638898,
      "updated": 1772638910
    },
    {
      "id": "69a852c20000000000f05e8f",
      "text": "\t\t$ $HOME/.copilot/copilot-instructions.md",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638915,
      "updated": 1772638921
    },
    {
      "id": "69a852ce0000000000f05e90",
      "text": "\t\t参考：https://docs.github.com/en/copilot/how-tos/copilot-cli/customize-copilot/add-custom-instructions#local-instructions",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638926,
      "updated": 1772638930
    },
    {
      "id": "69a852d20000000000f05e91",
      "text": "\t以下のような内容で書き込んでおけば、日本語で返事してくれるようになる",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638931,
      "updated": 1772639026
    },
    {
      "id": "69a853310000000000f05e92",
      "text": "\t\tcode:copilog-instructions.md",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772639026,
      "updated": 1772639040
    },
    {
      "id": "69a8533b0000000000f05e93",
      "text": "\t\t # Copilotの返答ルール",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772639036,
      "updated": 1772639044
    },
    {
      "id": "69a8533c0000000000f05e95",
      "text": "   - 特別な指示が無い限り、必ず日本語で回答すること",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772639036,
      "updated": 1772639042
    },
    {
      "id": "69a852360000000000f05e8a",
      "text": "\t\t[https://gyazo.com/2a4b359a7de41a0cf2a66a9b1e7cc32e]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772638775,
      "updated": 1772639069
    },
    {
      "id": "69a8535d0000000000f05e98",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1772639069,
      "updated": 1772639069
    }
  ]
}